Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:18.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}記者·七尾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩漿從魔界的入口處不斷噴涌而出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日的勇者們是否也是在這樣的地獄中一往直前呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}○聯繫你我○ 王都TV
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升 3000安培！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍是怎麼回事 看起來有些年代了卻如此鋒利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 全A
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有多遠了 加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 給我讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是百感交集 時到今日 我反而如此像個勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好？我可一直以勇者自居
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾·斬擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾 進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗 拉姆 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋 不要隨便略稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹什麼呢啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人守門的話 這群傢伙就會一擁而入了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 快點進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是勇者嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要什麼資格 你是個真正的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你一定要救出菲諾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是… 你可是我看好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾·切薩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 之後拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是吃虧不討好的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是上班時間 你在這幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙可擔心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 一起回店裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾 你不記得我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾 你覺得本大人..成為魔王好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於老爸被打倒 不是有很多人都失去了工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有很多造武器和防具的公司都倒閉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說大家都很煩惱..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 你完全沒有必要成為魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會逃的 我一定要奪回你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了 菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}再說了 你表情也太冷淡了吧 我教過你接客的基本是笑容了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給忘掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非..常..感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 回憶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔法道具店雷昂王都店的店員 菲諾·布拉德斯通！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞爾 本大人我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒過來了嗎 菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人為什麼會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 勞爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持住 菲諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人 不想成為..魔..王..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能放你去魔界！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞..爾..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 我不會讓你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲..諾..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞..爾..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲..諾..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 不適合 那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲諾你不是一路努力過來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天一直努力著 我是記得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容 你的努力 全都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人無語般的樂觀 但這又是多麼地耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:15:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點點不甘心 又非常羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是 要成為一名獨當一面的魔法道具店店員的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來！
